{"type": "article", "id": 10161, "title": "「 儿童节可以准备起来了」之 “Mickey Plays”", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-29T07:20:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235616a0w8jnxJsitDW2ZE.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近，Uniqlo 和 Disney 携手推出了一个叫做 “Mickey Plays” 的联名系列，包括 8 款男装和 4 款童装，作品以网球运动员 Novak Djokovic，Kei Nishikori，Shingo Kunieda 和职业高尔夫选手 Adam Scott 的场上姿态作为灵感来源，加上 Mickey 可爱的模样，整个作品看上去活泼又不失时尚度呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235612GAaPfZXv7d8kVnhL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235612E7LpIViq5a8BFOmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235613ieCHsDXSqBpjJRa6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235613qiwMElO8GhZsCajY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235613FEhR2A6tjfYwgeqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235614sRmGabCUFg586xAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235614aPclqHBzTZesvWD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235614DGJqIZxzCKBAXs3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}